_sText:
Hello

This css_unic_thelostbled , a medium size rescue hostages map.

In desert environnment, an anbandonned village with houses you can get in, castle wich is the location of the hostages, walls that you can climb on and jump and other many possibilities to ambush; The Ct have 2 ways to give assault  but  only one way is available  to put the hostages in security; spots to sniping in houses and corners, hidden places...

A map made for 24 players; more depends from your configuration,  action is guarantee with this map.

Nav points bots provided as usual.

Good Game
